item.title: Help Getting Server Online!
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

Your master coders must know nothing, setting a server up is the easiest part of hosting and creating servers a monkey could most likely do this.

Use a port checker to see if your server is have been port forwarding correctly and the port is open, a good place is; http://www.canyouseeme.org/.

If it says it’s offline, this could mean a few things, it could mean that your not running your server at all, it could mean that you didn’t port forward correctly, and it could mean your port isn’t open, you should check before you check the port to see if all these things are done correctly.

Read full topic
